      <h2 class="calc-tile-name">Bitcoin &amp; The Power Law</h2>
      <p class="calc-tile-question">What is the channel, and where does bitcoin sit inside it?</p>
      <p class="calc-tile-desc">An interactive view of the Power Law channel &mdash; floor, trend, upper band &mdash; across bitcoin's lifetime, with daily price overlaid. Toggle between linear-time (curves) and log-log (straight lines) to see the same model two ways. The foundational page that anchors the projections used elsewhere.</p>
