      <h2 class="calc-tile-name">The Bitcoin Retirement</h2>
      <p class="calc-tile-question">When can I retire on bitcoin?</p>
      <p class="calc-tile-desc">A scenario laboratory built on Power Law projections. Drag the sliders to explore three retirement questions: how much bitcoin do you need, when can you retire, on what income. The sustainability readout shows years lasted, real-terms stack value, and escape velocity.</p>
      <span class="calc-tile-cta">Explore scenarios</span>
