      <h2 class="calc-tile-name">Disciplined Rebalancing</h2>
      <p class="calc-tile-question">How can the Power Law channel itself become a discipline?</p>
      <p class="calc-tile-desc">A bounded protocol for retirement-wrapped bitcoin: sell at percentile triggers, rebuy at lower-percentile triggers. The Power Law channel becomes a set of observable conditions to act on rather than a model to merely believe in. Conditional projection, honest treatment of underperformance, no speculation about <em>where price is going</em>.</p>
      <span class="calc-tile-cta">Run the discipline</span>
    </a>

